Best Kava & Krat-Tea in South Florida
Welcome to Island Vibes Delray Beach
Our kava bar offers a tranquil environment where you can unwind and enjoy the calming effects of kava, a beverage made from the root of the kava plant. Whether you’re new to kava or a seasoned enthusiast, we provide a variety of drinks crafted to suit your preferences. With a cozy atmosphere, friendly staff, and a focus on connection, Islan Vibes is the perfect place to relax, socialize, and experience the benefits of this ancient Polynesian tradition.
“I’m always treated better than family. They are quick on service & aim to pleas.”
learn more
Who we are
try the best kava in town
Nestled in the heart of the city,
Island Vibes
Delray stands as the ultimate destination for relaxation and rejuvenation. Known for its serene ambiance and top-quality kava, this hidden gem serves up the finest brews made from handpicked roots, ensuring a smooth and calming experience. The friendly staff and cozy atmosphere invite guests to unwind, whether you’re looking to enjoy a solo retreat or socialize with friends. With a menu that caters to both kava enthusiasts and newcomers alike,
Island Vibes Delray
is the best place in town to experience the true essence of kava culture.
